{"tid":829623,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FGO喺TGS 2018拎咗優秀遊戲獎","createTime":"2018-09-20T14:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T12:24:47.000Z","uid":78070,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26d1e8008a1b49c622e2186d97cf8da6d15f016e","tid":829623,"uid":78070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/224743_f66c7b60402d0ee339475c8829740a84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F224743_f66c7b60402d0ee339475c8829740a84.jpg&h=cb4be8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFate/Grand Order，俗稱FGO，獲得本屆TGS優秀遊戲獎<br />\n其他獲獎的遊戲有Xenoblade 2，Super Mario: Odyssey，Monster Hunter: World，PKM: Sun &amp; Moon<br />\n<br />\n2018 日本遊戲大賞結果公佈！<br />\n年度遊戲：《Monster Hunter: World》！<br />\n経済産業大臣賞：Nintendo Switch 開發部<br />\n全球獎 日本作品部門：《塞爾達傳說 曠野之息》<br />\n全球獎 海外作品部門：《Call of Duty: WW2》<br />\n最佳銷售獎：《勇者鬥惡龍 11》<br />\n遊戲設計師大獎：《Gorogoa》<br />\n優秀獎：<br />\n&quot;Fate/Grand Order&quot;<br />\n&quot;Xenoblade 2&quot;<br />\n&quot;勇者鬥惡龍 11&quot;<br />\n&quot;UNDERTALE&quot;<br />\n&quot;Super Mario: Odyssey&quot;<br />\n&quot;Call of Duty: WW2<br />\n&quot;精靈寶可夢 究極日月&quot;<br />\n&quot;Splatoon 2&quot;<br />\n&quot;PLAYERUNKNOWN&rsquo;S BATTLEGROUNDS&quot;<br />\n&quot;Monster Hunter: World&quot;<br />\n&quot;Fortnite&quot;<br />\n<br />\n手機課金Game都可以拎獎，仲要係喺TGS呢啲國際級遊戲展，你怕唔怕俾人笑呀日本仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a382b2233abb10a52cf4fd089a423ae325fde06","tid":829623,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"有咩咁優秀&hellip;"},{"pid":"a25d764d83168fe02f970de874890a41b8719f9c","tid":829623,"uid":78070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a382b2233abb10a52cf4fd089a423ae325fde06"